item.title: My Workbench
item.description: As my first post, I wanted to show you my workbench where all the magic happens. I was looking around for a workbench I could just buy, but I never found exactly what I wanted at the price I wanted after 2 weeks of searching. I wanted 3 things: * Long enough to have a solder station, printer, and computer * A large light overhead * Have a working surface about counter high
